--- title: Fen2img keywords: fastai sidebar: home_sidebar summary: "A tool to generate chess board image from a Forsyth–Edwards Notation(FEN) string." description: "A tool to generate chess board image from a Forsyth–Edwards Notation(FEN) string." ---
{% raw %}
{% endraw %}

Install

pip install fen2img

How to use

here is an example:

{% raw %} 
fen2img('rnbqkbnr/pppppppp/8/8/8/8/PPPPPPPP/RNBQKBNR',
        board_style='brown', boards_path='fen2img/boards',
        piece_style='merida', pieces_path='fen2img/pieces')
{% endraw %}

*** The image files for above board and piece styles are copied from PgnViewer.
